{"tid":1706624,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"令到老師翻唔到工嘅方法","createTime":"2019-11-11T06:34:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T05:54:49.000Z","uid":179179,"like":14,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"9b509299c26804a65b56ef1d7ca316d58812e7a8","tid":1706624,"uid":179179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T06:34:15.000Z","msg":"就係破壞中學校， 唔洗多校門個啲就夠<br />\n<br />\n點解八大可以罷課但中小學唔洗，就係因為無人搞佢地，令到老師覺得有義務繼續翻工，同老師只需要早啲起身就趕到翻學<br />\n<br />\n雖然唔係好方法，但就可以破斧沉舟試一試，教協又唔出聲，教局又唔做野<br />\n<br />\n民意呢啲野，算啦 一早歸哂邊<br />\n警察殺人唔通藍絲會變黃<br />\n兄弟爬山，各有各做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2bb505e98d3f1891c8998c051a1aadc255b2a87","tid":1706624,"uid":179179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T06:34:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed6c3befecdd37a8d44b7b1756055d25ecabf1dc","tid":1706624,"uid":179179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T06:34:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab9bae06d41ee6ffda52fe8e8da4d2155f6c8e79","tid":1706624,"uid":116721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T06:35:02.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"756c3a9bdeffe3fca73523b19ab4a39984731d3d","tid":1706624,"uid":179179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T06:35:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"16b2d7ca62c98abd49e4dedece7c4af7a7d93fac","tid":1706624,"uid":179179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T06:36:16.000Z","msg":"啱聽就幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dad030d1d7c950b545650a750960387b41e46388","tid":1706624,"uid":143151,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T06:36:24.000Z","msg":"關撚事咩 爛咗個校門 佢哋一撚樣可以番工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\